data.description: Hard to find Horse Lover's Dream.  This is your daily get-a-way.  This well cared for and maintained home sits on 20 acres, south of Twin Falls.  The kitchen has a breakfast bar, pantry and lots of counter space.  The family room is nearly all windows on 2 walls giving you lots natural light and a great view.  The large master has a walk-in closet, dual vanity, jetted tub and a separate shower.  You'll also find a barn with electricity, 2 sheds, a tack room and a 2 bedroom, 1 bath guest house that was added in 2019...it has a full kitchen, bath, laundry and has electric heat and a/c... all the comforts of home for your guests or an air bnb for a little extra income.  The entire 20 acres has a perimeter fencing, with several pasture areas fenced within the 20 acres.
